{"tid":2248618,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【是是旦旦】明珠台預告播2014《哥斯拉》 最後播左98年《哥斯拉》","createTime":"2020-10-18T17:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T17:24:31.000Z","uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd1ba902613cd8e13e427fa55b6ce5fd2524068","tid":2248618,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T17:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/10/1603006165_uL-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F10%2F1603006165_uL-1280w.jpg&h=f1a65d86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少人都以為周六播的是由「緋紅女巫」伊莉莎伯奧遜主演的《哥斯拉》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日明珠台晚上9點半的周末大電影時段，播出1998年版本的《哥斯拉》，然而不少網民發現「貨不對版」！<br />\n<br />\n事緣無綫早前播出的預告片是2014年的《哥斯拉》，此片由「緋紅女巫」伊莉莎伯奧遜（Elizabeth Olsen）及「快銀」亞倫強森（Aaron Taylor-Johnson）主演，惟昨晚播出的竟然是98年版本，翻查明珠台的節目表，簡介也是98年電影《哥斯拉》內容。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/10/1603006171_c0-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F10%2F1603006171_c0-1280w.jpg&h=cbfea57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過網民發現播出的哥斯拉與2014年的不同&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/10/1603006680_9z-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F10%2F1603006680_9z-1280w.png&h=f79cfd4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明珠台節目表簡介也是按98年的《哥斯拉》寫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不少網民對此感到好笑，因而在網上開PO討論。他們不少人都留言謂︰「大家都是哥斯拉，不用分得這麼細」、「我以為我睇錯預告」、「我睇睇下都覺唔妥 冇咗緋紅女神」、「 睇頭幾分鐘，點解好似未睇過嘅，再睇多陣，點解尚連奴會上電視嘅喂。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/10/1603006182_Vb-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F10%2F1603006182_Vb-1280w.png&h=2ac342e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/10/1603006174_kH-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F10%2F1603006174_kH-1280w.png&h=5472201b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/10/1603006186_Dt-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F10%2F1603006186_Dt-1280w.png&h=2b5f3c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/10/1603006178_br-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F10%2F1603006178_br-1280w.png&h=cef9c10a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}